---
// src/pages/_site-updates/2026-07-12-pricing-cro-pass.astro
export const updateMeta = {
  date: '2026-07-12',
  title: 'Pricing page conversion pass: honest trial CTA, risk reversal, Founders scarcity',
  tags: ['pricing', 'cro', 'conversion'],
};
---
<article class="border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] pl-6">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">July 12, 2026</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Conversion pass on <a href="/pricing" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">/pricing</a> to reduce trial-funnel drop-off.</p>
  <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
    <li><strong>CTA honesty:</strong> plan buttons and the closing CTA now read "Start your 14-day free trial," with a card-honesty line ("Card required to start. Cancel anytime before day 14 and you are not charged.") directly under each plan button so the trial expectation is set before the click, not at the checkout wall.</li>
    <li><strong>Risk reversal at the decision point:</strong> the closing CTA now leads with setup speed plus the cancel-before-day-14 reassurance, and reinforces "No percentage of your sales, ever."</li>
    <li><strong>Founders scarcity made visible:</strong> the "first 100 founders" limit now appears at the discounted price on eligible cards and in the hero, not only in the FAQ.</li>
    <li><strong>Trial FAQ tightened</strong> to state full access, the card requirement, and the no-charge-on-cancel guarantee in one clear answer.</li>
  </ul>
</article>
